  "text": "where the rotation matrix C T (q) projects vectors expressed with respect to frame {S} to frame {G}. Note that since S is the unit vector direction of a line on the x-y plane of the laser sensor frame, it can be written as Employing (11) and [CITATION_1] , the measurement error is:",
